                    </p>

                    <h4 class="mb-3">5. Your Rights</h4>
                    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-4">
                        <li class="list-group-item">View and edit your profile details.</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">Delete your account or request data removal.</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">Contact us for privacy concerns or issues.</li>
                    </ul>

